    <item>
      <title>中国大宗商品公司首当其冲受到经济放缓的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/chinese-commodities-firms-bear-the-brunt-of-a-slowing-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国工业利润显示，大宗商品生产商将在 2024 年底处于垫底位置。今年的情况也不容乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/chinese-commodities-firms-bear-the-brunt-of-a-slowing-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 02:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 引发竞争担忧，日本芯片股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/japan-s-chip-shares-sink-as-deepseek-triggers-competition-fear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 获得关注，包括爱德万测试株式会社在内的日本芯片相关类股大幅下跌，引发人们担心该应用将威胁美国的技术领导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/japan-s-chip-shares-sink-as-deepseek-triggers-competition-fear</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 01:58:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰放宽签证规定，允许访客远程工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/new-zealand-eases-visa-rules-to-allow-visitors-to-work-remotely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰放宽了签证规定，允许外国游客在该国远程工作，因为该国依靠旅游业来推动经济复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/new-zealand-eases-visa-rules-to-allow-visitors-to-work-remotely</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 01:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本银行股因日本央行加息刺激盈利乐观情绪而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/japan-s-bank-shares-rise-as-boj-rate-hike-spurs-profit-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行将关键政策利率上调至 17 年来最高水平后，日本银行的股价因市场乐观预期上涨，其盈利能力将改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/japan-s-bank-shares-rise-as-boj-rate-hike-spurs-profit-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 01:46:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称廉价石油和高运费使俄罗斯原油供应持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/goldman-says-cheap-oil-high-freight-keeps-russian-crude-flowing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团表示，美国对俄罗斯石油工业实施的全面制裁不太可能导致产量受到“重大打击”，因为更高的运费和俄罗斯廉价的原油支撑了贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/goldman-says-cheap-oil-high-freight-keeps-russian-crude-flowing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 01:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普首次贸易限制措施削弱市场人气，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普首次实施制裁和关税，凸显全球经济和贸易面临的风险，导致油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 23:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 助力中国人工智能发展，亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市上涨，部分原因是对中国人工智能的乐观情绪，不受唐纳德特朗普对哥伦比亚征收关税导致其他地区风险偏好降低的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对哥伦比亚征收关税后，美元本周开局走强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/dollar-starts-week-on-front-foot-after-trump-s-colombia-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令对拒绝允许被驱逐的移民入境的哥伦比亚征收关税，随后美元在本周初小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/dollar-starts-week-on-front-foot-after-trump-s-colombia-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 21:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普扰乱关税观点 债券交易员将焦点转向美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/bond-traders-shift-focus-to-fed-as-trump-shadows-the-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在债券市场，唐纳德·特朗普上任的第一周至少没有人们担心的那么不稳定。交易员们希望美联储的最新举措也能带来同样的效果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/bond-traders-shift-focus-to-fed-as-trump-shadows-the-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
